summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of the suit to condemn certain portions of block 7, 8 and 9, Motor Line Addition to the City of Seattle, for the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of North 45th Street under Ordinance No. 20061, Cause No. 70475, insofar as the same affects Lot 15, Block 7; Lots 15 and 18, Block 8; and Lots 15 and 18, Block 9, all in Motor Line Addition to the City of Seattle.
